{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "story_bpipe_set_1", "eventName": "難行長路", "entryType": "NONE", "storyCode": null, "avgTag": "幕間", "storyName": "難行長路", "storyInfo": "離開維多利亞的風笛，歷經磨難，意識到自己必須試著找一下幫手。她第一時間想到了身在龍門的陳。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_lungmen_station", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$suspenseful_intro", "key": "$suspenseful_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "11:41 P.M. 天氣/陰"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "龍門7區外 入城關口"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$drift"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_015_lmg", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  星熊督察，你總算來啦！", "name": "近衛局成員"}, "figure_art": "char_015_lmg"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  唉，我可是脫鞋脫了一半，就給你小子一通電訊叫出來，大晚上跑過大半個龍門。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ——所以，你說的人呢？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_015_lmg"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  咳，抓、抓住了！現在正關在臨時監室裡。", "name": "近衛局成員"}, "figure_art": "char_015_lmg"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  抓了？幾個人抓的？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_015_lmg"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  呃，就我和另一個執勤的兄弟......", "name": "近衛局成員"}, "figure_art": "char_015_lmg"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......你說的，那是個維多利亞士兵，手裡還拿著挺嚇人的兵器。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_015_lmg"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我也搞不懂......", "name": "近衛局成員"}, "figure_art": "char_015_lmg"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我跟阿平還沒走近，她就丟掉了武器，舉著雙手揮了老半天，嘴裡還大聲喊著“我在這裡”，簡直跟生怕我們看不見一樣。", "name": "近衛局成員"}, "figure_art": "char_015_lmg"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  督察，我在這關口當了幾年差，真沒見過這種偷渡客。", "name": "近衛局成員"}, "figure_art": "char_015_lmg"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#2"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  沒事，我去會會她。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#2"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  哦，對了，你在電訊裡說，她還喊了什麼話？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#2"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_015_lmg"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  她大炎官話講得很差......但聽起來似乎是，陳......陳？", "name": "近衛局成員"}, "figure_art": "char_015_lmg"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  搞不好是我聽錯。", "name": "近衛局成員"}, "figure_art": "char_015_lmg"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  啊......哈。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  行了，我有數。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_cellroomA", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snapping", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.2, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$relax_intro", "key": "$relax_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  嗚哇，好亮——咦，終於有人來了？", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#4", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  嗯，來問幾個問題。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#4"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  這是......審訊？", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#4"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  算是吧。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#4"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#3"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  唉，以前都是我審別人，突然換到被審問的位置上，還真不太習慣。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#3"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#4"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  那你還乖乖交了武器......沒想過逃出去？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#4"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  從這裡出去應該還蠻簡單的......就算不用破城矛也......", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  咳咳，不，我不是這個意思！我忘了你是在審我......呃，我沒想過要跑啊，我是自願在這待著的！", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#4"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  為什麼？很少見人喜歡蹲大獄。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#4"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  倒也不是想被關著啦。只是，我聽說硬闖關口的話，會有警察來抓我......在龍門是叫近衛局對吧？", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我就想找你們，所以用了個最快的方法。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  找誰？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  陳陳......我是說，陳。她是在近衛局吧？好像已經是......警司？", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  唉，好可惜，我本來還以為她得到消息會自己過來。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  你和你說的這位陳警司有什麼關係？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我們是好朋友啊，她在維多利亞上學的時候，我們是同學。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  哪所學校？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  呃，皇家近衛學校。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  這麼說，你是士官？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......退役之前是。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  一名維多利亞退役士官，身穿制服，夜闖另一個國家邊境城市的入城關口，並且還拿著制式武器——", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  是去除了彈射功能的！", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......但保留著填彈裝置，依然具有很強的爆破能力。沒錯吧？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  （小聲）按照規定，我的確應該將破城矛上繳......", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#4", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  這麼說，你不是正常退役？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#4"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#4", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ............", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#4", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#3", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  這麼快就被問出來了啊。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#3"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  唉，早知道會有這一天，我上訊問學理論課的時候就該更努力一點的。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#3"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#4", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#3", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  你很想隱瞞自己的退役過程？小姐，如果你是逃兵，我這就該打電話叫人來了。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#4"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#4", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  不，請別叫人——", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 70.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我、我真的退役了，我向你保證！", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我會試著解釋一下，但是，有些資訊我實在沒法在這裡透露。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  先說說看。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$drift_intro", "key": "$drift_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  好吧，事情是這樣的。三個月前，我還在軍隊裡，我們小隊當時在追查一個案件。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  查案過程......呃......", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我只能說，因為查這個案件，我們小隊目前還活著......不，還能自由行動的，只剩下我一個。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#2", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  抱歉，這回憶一定很慘烈。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#2"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#2", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  謝謝你的理解。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#2", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  不過，我有一點不明白。你連命都差點沒了，那幫維多利亞軍隊的老頭子不該給你頒上一堆獎章嗎？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#2"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#2", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  獎勵？算啦，案子沒查完，我從來沒想過。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#2", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#3", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  但至少......我以為他們能多派些人來幫我繼續追查。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#3"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#2", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#3", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  結果沒有？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#2"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#2", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  很令人驚訝是不是？警官，我比你更想不明白。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我一開始試著找了很多人。從半島郡駐軍開始，他們每一個都在安撫我，讓我等待上級的命令，允諾我會儘快增派人手。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我聽從指示，結果發現時間越耗越久，調查卻全無進展。於是我決定繞開地方駐軍，直接聯絡倫蒂尼姆。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  這個過程不算太容易，好在我之前累積了一些怎麼跟駐軍打交道的經驗，並且一路上總能遇上好心人。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  最後，我成功抵達了距離倫蒂尼姆最近的一處軍營——", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  就是在那裡，我做出了退役的決定。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#2", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  因為他們還是沒有幫你？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#2"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#2", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#3", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  長官，伯爵，大公爵......他們可能有別的苦衷吧。反正他們這麼跟我說，我全聽進去了，直到那一天......", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#3"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我無意中聽見，中校在和另一個我不認識的軍官談論對我的安排。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#3"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  是的，我沒想到——", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#3"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  距離事件發生過去整整三十七天，我沒等來增援，只等來了一紙調令。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#3"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#2", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#3", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#2"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  你心裡肯定很不好受。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#2"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#2", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  嗯......我的心情很複雜。難過？還是失望，或者憤怒......我說不上來。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  在得知這個消息的時候，我的腦子一片空白，唯一的念頭是慶幸自己把破城矛放在了訓練室，而不是帶在手邊。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  不然的話，你會動手？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  也不會吧......大概。畢竟，我始終記得自己的職責。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  同樣的，作為一名維多利亞軍人，我必須服從命令。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  可是......警官，在那一刻，我發現我做不到。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#2", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  沒有一支軍隊能容忍抗拒命令的士兵。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#2"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#2", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  是啊。就這樣，我很快想通了，我要在他們決定我的去向之前，自己離開軍隊。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8"}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#2", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  他們答應放你走？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#2"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#2", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  退役手續還算順利啦，以前隊長和陳陳都抱怨過我太倔，中校他們當然怎麼勸阻都沒用。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#2", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  可是，就在我去軍營交還武器的時候，我遇到了襲擊。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......襲擊？犯人是誰？你在追查的人嗎？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  很有可能。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我不是沒想過，他們為什麼會選擇在軍營動手，明明之前一個多月都沒有管我......", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  會不會是敵人最終還是滲透進了軍隊高層？又或者根本就......", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#3", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  唉，這些都不重要了。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#3"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我打退了其中幾個，可他們人還是很多，我不得不拿著破城矛匆匆逃了出來。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#3"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#3", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  之後呢？你就這樣逃出了維多利亞？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#9", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  說逃......也沒錯，哈哈，這一路真是挺狼狽的。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#9"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我知道那群人很難纏，自然不敢回家，我不想讓鬼魂也纏上媽媽他們。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  軍隊更是回不去了，找警察也只會給他們添麻煩，我想來想去......", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  只能找同學了？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  嗯，是呀，陳陳答應過的，我有事沒事都能來找她！", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......哈哈。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#3", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  欸，警官，你笑什麼呀？", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#3"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#3", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  沒事。所以，你來了龍門。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  她確實是在龍門，我沒搞錯吧？去年年初的拜年電訊還是從這個地方發出來的呀。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  繼續說說你為何要硬闖關口吧。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  無論有沒有人在後頭追殺，你好歹也是維多利亞公民，不至於連張正常的車票都買不起吧？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#3", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......還真買不起。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#3"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#2", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#3", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  啊？維多利亞職業軍人的收入還不及龍門街頭仔？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#2"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#2", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#3", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  沒有啦......", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#3"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  那個......我的錢包和護照都丟在萊塔尼亞了。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#3"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#3", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......我是不是該佩服你？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ——被炸得一點不剩了。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我確實該佩服你。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  不光錢包，我也差一點點就被炸飛啦。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  那時候我才剛離開維多利亞，蹭了一支商隊的車橫穿萊塔尼亞。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  剛入境沒兩天，車子路過一座小城市，當地一位子爵挺熱情地招待了我們，還安排我們住進了最好的酒店。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  到了傍晚的時候，其他人去赴宴了，我一個人待在分給我的豪華套間裡，有服務員送了一份免費的晚餐過來。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我吃了幾口，總覺得萊塔尼亞菜太精緻了，我吃不太習慣，就想著出門找個農貿市場溜達幾圈。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......沒想到才剛到樓下，轟隆一聲，我房間的窗框就砸到了我跟前，而且整個都變了形。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  這炸得還真狠。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#3", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  是呀，就算是我，被從十幾層高的房間裡炸飛出來，也可能會沒命吧？", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#3"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#3", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#3", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......只是可能？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#3"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#3", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  已經很嚴重了呀！真沒想到萊塔尼亞也這麼水深火熱。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  嗯，看來你從精神到身體都比那倒楣的窗框結實多了。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5"}, {"id": 239, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#3", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  欸？多謝......誇獎？", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#3"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#2", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#3", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  說起來，你知道是誰要炸你？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#2"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#2", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  不知道啊。我加入商隊沒幾天，有力出力，應該沒什麼仇家吧？", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  其實......我也沒那麼在乎這一個問題的答案。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  自從開始查這個案子，謎團越來越多，就沒有什麼豁然開朗的時候，我都習慣啦。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  那麼，你來龍門，是想讓你朋友撐你？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5"}, {"id": 249, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  唔，我不需要別人保護，只是想問問陳陳願不願意幫我。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}, {"id": 251, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  哦？你還想著回維多利亞查案？哪怕這麼多人要殺你？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5"}, {"id": 253, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#9", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  沒錯。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#9"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#9", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  還真一點猶豫都沒有。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5"}, {"id": 257, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  呼......", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8"}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  從維多利亞到龍門，我走了幾個月。但凡我有半點猶豫，這條路我都走不下去。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我答應過，我要把真相帶到所有人面前。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8"}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  不知道真相在哪，我就去找——", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  敵人不讓我說話，我偏要說。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8"}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  離開維多利亞，我沒有回頭。可要是哪天我做好了回去的準備，我更不會有一絲動搖。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#2", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  不怕嗎？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#2"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#2", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  怕。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  嗯，我信你。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  欸？", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  把不怕死掛在嘴邊的戰士，要嘛是在說大話，要嘛是還沒想明白。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我相信你做好了該做的準備，也相信你沒有說假話。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5"}, {"id": 275, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  這麼說，你會幫我聯絡陳......陳警司？", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  給，這袋子裡有幾個叉燒包。涼差不多了，將就一下還能吃。在荒地裡趕了這麼久路，你該餓壞了吧？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5"}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  就算是像你這麼強悍的瓦伊凡，該吃飯還得吃飯。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  唔嗯......", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#9"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......真好吃......", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#9"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  呃，不對啊，這也是訊問流程？", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#9"}, {"id": 287, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  流程？早結束了。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5"}, {"id": 289, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我還以為你會問我一些我和陳陳過去的事，來驗證我有沒有說謊......", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5"}, {"id": 291, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  沒必要。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5"}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  該知道的，我早知道了。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5"}, {"id": 294, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  你的意思是......", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5"}, {"id": 296, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  咦，等等，我想起來了，我也知道你，你是近衛局的星......星......", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2"}, {"id": 298, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  星......星？哈哈，最好還是別這麼叫我，尤其是別在她們面前這麼叫。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5"}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  這樣吧，風笛小姐，按照規矩，麻煩你再多在這屋待一會，我先出去一下，見個人。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5"}, {"id": 301, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "move", "xpos": 300.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_indoor_3", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_308_swire_1#3"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  審完了？", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "char_308_swire_1#3"}, {"id": 316, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$relax_intro", "key": "$relax_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "char_308_swire_1#3"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "xpos": 200.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5", "name2": "char_308_swire_1#3", "fadetime": 0.7}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5", "name2": "char_308_swire_1#3", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  既然好奇，為什麼不進來？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5"}, {"id": 327, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5", "name2": "char_308_swire_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......有什麼值得好奇的？", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "char_308_swire_1"}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  羅德島的人都在路上了，她在這裡根本待不長。", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "char_308_swire_1"}, {"id": 330, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#2", "name2": "char_308_swire_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  算算時間，他們是該來了。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#2"}, {"id": 332, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#2", "name2": "char_308_swire_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  哼，那條仆街龍，這陣子也不知道又在哪裡逍遙，害我們在這裡加班。", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "char_308_swire_1#5"}, {"id": 334, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5", "name2": "char_308_swire_1#5", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  要是老陳聽說老同學千里迢迢找來，一點都不著急是不可能的。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5"}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  她雖然不說，但對朋友一向仗義，Missy，你又不是不知道。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5", "name2": "char_308_swire_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......她的朋友，關我什麼事？", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "char_308_swire_1"}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  還有你，明明剛接到消息就第一時間給羅德島發了信，為什麼還要費這工夫審訊？唱黑臉很過癮？", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "char_308_swire_1"}, {"id": 340, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5", "name2": "char_308_swire_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  那麼多小子看著呢，都是當差的人，流程還是要好好走完的。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5"}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  再說了，你就不想打探打探，老陳之後可能會捲進什麼新的危險裡去？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5"}, {"id": 343, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5", "name2": "char_308_swire_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......不想知道。", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "char_308_swire_1#5"}, {"id": 345, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5", "name2": "char_308_swire_1#6", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  唉，煩死了！等裡面那傢伙被羅德島的人接走，你就給我好好彙報清楚......不許偷懶！", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "char_308_swire_1#6"}, {"id": 347, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5", "name2": "char_308_swire_1#6", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  哈哈，好。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5"}, {"id": 349, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  看，羅德島的幹員來領人了——", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "char_136_hsguma_ns_1#5"}, {"id": 350, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  欸欸欸，什麼？！", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2"}, {"id": 356, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  陳陳竟然已經不在龍門近衛局了，你們讓我去一個別的地方等著？", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2"}, {"id": 357, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  呃，那家公司叫什麼來著......", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2"}, {"id": 358, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ——羅、德、島？", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2"}, {"id": 359, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}